@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="card shadow-sm p-4">
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-primary">About MediLink</h2>
    <p>
        MediLink is a healthcare management platform designed to improve communication and coordination
        between patients, doctors, and administrators.
    </p>
    <p>
        The system allows patients to view doctors and appointments, doctors to manage their schedules,
        and administrators to oversee healthcare operations efficiently.
    </p>
    <p>
        MediLink focuses on usability, accessibility, and organized healthcare management in one system.
    </p>
</div>